<topic id="adding_or_customizing_an_existing_view">
    <title>Adding a new Side-View</title>
    <body>
        <p>A
            <b>Workspace Access</b>
             plugin type can contribute a new side view to Oxygen. For example this
            <b>plugin.xml</b>
             plugin descriptor file defines a new view ID called
            <b>SampleWorkspaceAccessToolbarID</b>
             :
            <xref
                href="https://github.com/oxygenxml/sample-plugin-workspace-access/blob/master/plugin.xml"
                scope="external" format="html"/>
             . </p>
        <p>Once the new view ID is declared, the Java code of the plugin can add content to the view
            using the
            <xref
                href="https://github.com/oxygenxml/sample-plugin-workspace-access/blob/master/src/main/java/com/oxygenxml/sdksamples/workspace/CustomWorkspaceAccessPluginExtension.java"
                format="html" scope="external">
                <b>pluginWorkspaceAccess.addViewComponentCustomizer</b>
            </xref>
             API.</p>
    </body>
</topic>
